I trust the Relais & Chateux brand, and it lived up to its luxurious standard.	The second visit found me in a standard room... also spacious and refined.	I had a standard room and it was very spacious.	Nice views of the city from our balcony (in a standard room).	When asked why I chose to bring them to Bacchus at the Wedgewood - I said for the same reason - I value them and more importantly, trust them to do the right thing - all the time.	Our experience in 2006 does not support the reputation that the hotel now enjoys.